OL,5, Andy Montgomery, his wife and          
OL,6, daughters, 11 and 13, got up at 3am on 
OL,7, Monday to get to Gatwick in good time  
OL,8, for their flight to Rome.              
OL,10,FBut he isn't going anywhere now, after 
OL,11,Fhis flight was cancelled and the       
OL,12,Fairline couldn't find him an           
OL,13,Falternative.                           
OL,15,F"It's absolutely diabolical," he said. 
OL,17,FThe Montgomeries are just one of       
OL,18,Fhundreds of families left with their   
OL,19,Fholiday plans in tatters after flights 
OL,20,Fwere cancelled.                        
